spanGrp.span: nam longbini nap pune punen soo usili timaleh soo són lasen, san naana
I want to tell a story about a child with his mother, his mama
mi wantem talem wan stori abaot wan pikinini wetem mama blong hem
o.k. timaleh man kiye són san naana kolom du lan vele soo koloo kolom du van lon duut muru
o.k., this boy with his mother, the two lived in one land, the two went a little bit into the bush
o.k. pikinini man ya wetem mama blong hem, tufala i stap long wan vilij, tufala i stap long bus lelebet
vanten ngyee lam du lan vele, tyenem tyenem me pwet mwe e tyenem kekeli muru gon
people went to the land, the village was only small
ol man oli stap long vilij, vilij ya i wan smol vilij nomo
mwe pwet me mee lereh muru
it came down to the beach a little bit
i stap i kam daon smol
koloo kolom du van lon duut lon poap
the two went into the bush into the cave
tufala i stap long bus long kev
timaleh man kumuru ye san naana me e kiikyee
that small boy, his mother was a snake
pikinini boy ya mama blong hem em i snek
a kolom du a timaleh man muru ye me mee mobo ngiye
and the two went on, and the small boy became big now
be tufala i stap be smol boe ya i kam i bigwan nao
a san naana mu du mwe kie mane, mwe kie ka, timaleh!
and his mother talked to him, she said, Child!
mo mama blong hem i stap talem long hem, se, pikinini!
timaleh! akop pwet akop du kop bwengbang van mane sam biibilen ngyee
Child! you should keep playing with your friends
pikinini! bae yu stap, bae yu stap pleple i go wetem ol fren blong yu
kop bwengbang van tyenem ke tobo kop van kop bwengbang mane sam biibilen ngyee
you should play in direction of the big village, you should lay with your friends
yu pleple i go long bigfela vilij yu go yu pleple wetem ol fren blong yu
kop bwengbang van, yaa be van bu du sólóó ka piipili kop kuolimee tyenem
you should play on, when the sun goes down so that it becomes red, you should come home
yu pleple i go, san i stap go daon blong i red, yu kambak long haos
saka kon bwengbang van mát ten
you should not play on longer
yu no pleple i go tumas
a saka kon idi sam biibilen ngyee lan mee lon sadoo tyenem
and you should not take your friends so that they come to our home
be yu no tekem ol fren blong yu oli kam long haos blong yumitu
kop van gon monok, kop kuoli
you should go then, you should come back
yu go finis, yu kam bak
timaleh man muru ye mwi idi lon san notnoten

smol pikinini ya i tekem long tingting blong hem
me mee mwe bwengbang mane san biibilen ngyee timaleh man ngyee
he came and played with his male friends
i kam i pleple wetem ol fren blong hem, ol boe
lam van lam bwengbang lam ko okingyee ye, la lam pinin

oli go oli pleple, oli handing long ol ples ya, oli rus
lam bwengbang vaa te lehe yaa te van te pwet ti piipili mwe kuolimee tyenem

me van tyenem, lon poap kiye teteh
